import product1 from '../../images/product-1.jpg'
import product2 from '../../images/product-2.jpg'
import product3 from '../../images/product-3.jpg'


export const productData = [
    {
        img: product1,
        alt: 'Sign',
        name: 'Neon Sign',
        desc: 'Design your own sign',
        price: 'TBD',
        button: 'Cotiza'
    },
    {
        img: product2,
        alt: '5m Flex',
        name: '5m Flex',
        desc: '5m of neon flex',
        price: '240 pesos',
        button: 'Cotiza'
    },
    {
        img: product3,
        alt: '50m Flex',
        name: '50m Flex',
        desc: 'A 50m neon flex',
        price: '2,000 pesos',
        button: 'Cotiza'
    }
]
